HEADWORD: blazing-star
<hw>blazing-star</hw> <pos>n.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>any of various
North American plants of the genus Liatris having racemes or panicles of
small discoid flower heads.</def>⟦br⟧
<syn><b>Syn. --</b> blazing star, button snakeroot, gayfeather,
snakeroot.</syn>⟦br⟧
